{"tid":531504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「細哨」朗拿甸奴結束職業生涯　巴塞官方發文感謝貢獻","createTime":"2018-01-17T01:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T03:04:07.000Z","uid":29625,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"7f09102c26ca0872289b5ab30edf6a982db65d23","tid":531504,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:54:42.000Z","msg":"【足球】「細哨」朗拿甸奴結束職業生涯　巴塞官方發文感謝貢獻<br />\n撰文：\t陳雋堯 發佈日期：2018-01-17 09:25 最後更新日期：2018-01-17 09:25<br />\n<br />\n「細哨」朗拿甸奴結束職業生涯！他的經理人兼哥哥證實，這位曾替巴西奪得2002年世界盃、帶領巴塞隆拿橫掃歐洲球壇的前金球獎得主已正式退役。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1134845/xlarge/117497ff55f0241c39c229f9aab0ebe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1134845%2Fxlarge%2F117497ff55f0241c39c229f9aab0ebe5.jpg&h=26cd3523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朗拿甸奴（右）與李華度（左）及朗拿度組成3R組合，協助巴西奪得2002世界盃。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n朗拿甸奴的哥哥接受訪問時表示：「他已經停下來，職業生涯已結束。我們將在巴西、歐洲和亞洲舉行一些活動，當然，我們也會和巴西國家隊安排退役儀式。舉辦的時間將會在俄羅斯世界盃後，也許在8月。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1134846/xlarge/7cf7bda6999e90c1a0d828786ac4b987.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1134846%2Fxlarge%2F7cf7bda6999e90c1a0d828786ac4b987.jpg&h=bcc60465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朗拿甸奴（中）是2004及2005世界足球先生得主。（視覺中國）<br />\n<br />\n現年37歲的朗拿甸奴在巴西球會甘美奧開始職業生涯，他能勝任前場多個位置，包括進攻中場，翼鋒及正前鋒。2001年，他離開祖國加盟法甲球會巴黎聖日耳門，登陸歐洲球壇。在翌年的世界盃決賽周中，他與朗拿度及李華度組成令人聞風喪膽的「3R」組合，最終帶領巴西在決賽周7戰全勝奪冠，而他在8強對英格蘭「笠死」對方門將施文的入球更成為賽事經典之一。他總共替國家隊上陣97次，共射入33球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1134847/xlarge/abcc6349bae3134c4335f87d22b9b9a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1134847%2Fxlarge%2Fabcc6349bae3134c4335f87d22b9b9a8.jpg&h=e1918af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在效力巴塞年間，朗拿甸奴（下）與剛出道的美斯（上）合作無間。（視覺中國）<br />\n<br />\n由於在世界盃的出色表現，西甲班霸巴塞隆拿於2003年以3000歐元將他簽下，朗拿甸奴亦迎來其職業生涯巔峰。在效力巴塞5個球季間，他共替球會贏得2個西甲冠軍、2個西班牙超級杯冠軍和1個歐聯冠軍，出色表現也令他在2005年包攬世界足球先生和金球獎，奠定其巴塞傳奇球星地位。其後由於哥迪奧拿上任，他亦不獲留用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1134848/xlarge/2e41e6f18f8f788fb093a31b60272283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1134848%2Fxlarge%2F2e41e6f18f8f788fb093a31b60272283.jpg&h=3614e604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朗拿甸奴（右2）近年返回巴西發展，曾在世冠盃與中國國家隊隊長鄭智（左2）對疊。（視覺中國）<br />\n<br />\n離開西班牙後，朗拿甸奴加盟意甲球會AC米蘭，並贏得一次意甲冠軍。及後他回國效力多間球會，包括法林明高、明尼路及富明尼斯，亦曾短暫效力墨西哥球會克雷塔羅，而他在2015年替富明尼斯出戰後便沒有再代表球會上陣。<br />\n<br />\n在得悉細哨退役消息後，巴塞隆拿官方Twitter發文，感謝他效力時的貢獻：「魯營球場永遠微笑着的魔術師，感謝你做的一切！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1134849/xlarge/5237a08c4a75eba5e495524e5837f88f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1134849%2Fxlarge%2F5237a08c4a75eba5e495524e5837f88f.jpg&h=7a5688aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴塞隆拿在官方Twitter貼文，感謝朗拿甸奴的貢獻。（網上截圖）"},{"pid":"10aa5454a3fb0f17b22dd4d3b6b25e1e4ef63d8a","tid":531504,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e57338c37c07bbc9beff2082bd575f0570f543b","tid":531504,"uid":7090,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:59:27.000Z","msg":"3000歐玩就簽到佢<br />\n想簽佢返黎做我屋企鐘點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a988250d8c86b79461fe2df86b2009b41b338d4e","tid":531504,"uid":2033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ca1def42ac3099a5f254b51f1418e4d18733b8","tid":531504,"uid":43809,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"冰火版真天魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0f377906335fb49d6dc1f763df4ec642727756","tid":531504,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1e89a67ac0fae7a63b48f3d641c3381da26f65","tid":531504,"uid":143582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:11:40.000Z","msg":"等睇人用細哨踩美斯"},{"pid":"ff2f41d53ed6a65dd447b277b744dd4454611a97","tid":531504,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:11:57.000Z","msg":"捧完歐聯就gg左<br />\n其實個場表現都差，不過拿臣出馬，享利又敗家。.."},{"pid":"c9af8ec21f00e1f94f57b2edf385769110482b50","tid":531504,"uid":743,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:14:46.000Z","msg":"扭波控波真係世界第一 <br />\n因為佢先鍾意睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db95093c45c79660419b2f008b395ecb9d3d905a","tid":531504,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:29:29.000Z","msg":"3000歐元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9738c05cc104b8427fe14ce6a0aac2a76c57b4f4","tid":531504,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"細哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e1ddc85a7300573bc45c6d010f8af51ee76a14","tid":531504,"uid":28758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"曾在世冠盃與中國國家隊隊長鄭智對疊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae974728ddeccb23dd2f7fbfd02fdfa0d236938","tid":531504,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"文呢？"},{"pid":"81480f8c4b4e9842cf00c2a26efc7eb206214bb2","tid":531504,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"cited